name: Bambietta Basterbine (Bleach)
description:
This is my first LoRA, in which I try to depict one of my favourite Bleach characters. Activation tag is "bambie"; "bambietta" in newer versions.

If you have bad renders, I recommend to reduce the weight of the LoRA (see examples).

I'm going to retrain it after new season of Bleach TYBW with Bambietta provides better dataset.

Also you can support me on ko-fi and Patreon.
